Description

This is a little batch game where you can make your own maps or play inculded maps (like night or tunnel).This uses %last% system what means that you can make collisions into centered block.You can also play with your friend (Player 1 WASD Player 2 8456).This game also needs CHOICE.exe. If you don't have choice.exe ,you need to download it here : (when you don't have this ,game crashes).More features are coming soon.

What's new : First relaese

Go to this link for update : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EGwpH16ypBc

Download : Not available for this version, check newer versions

Extract file to your folder and read readme to get more information.
Then open Start_game.bat.

If you want to share your own maps,then comment mapname.cmd and mapname_ifcheck.cmd components or upload and give download link in comments.If you had any bugs in this game then comment. EVERYONE CAN COMMENT!

*****************************************************************************
Thanks for watching!
